node.text:
Here they are! Our contestants still on the Road to Orlando 👑

Voting to help decide our Top 20 Miss #HootersPageant contestants starts tomorrow. Keep an eye on our stories for details!

node.text:
Use code GETDELIVERY for $0 delivery fees on HootersOnTheFly.com or in the Hooters app! Only on Mondays! 

Offer valid only for orders placed at HootersOnTheFly.com or the Hooters app.  Minimum order of $25 required. Offer valid every Monday between 7/12/21 and 7/26/21.

node.text:
Do you have your Pageant game plan ready? 

Tickets are on sale now for our Miss Hooters Pageant in Orlando on 7/29! But if you can’t make it, we’ll be streaming all the action live at your local Hooters. 

Head to the link in our bio for all the details!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Hooters on July 12, 2021. May be an image of food and text that says 'BUD LIGHT Boneless. Beer. Bundle. Booyah! $13.99 only 10 Boneless Wings, Curly Fries and a pint of domestic beer.'.

node.text:
We got a hot deal for you. 🔥The Boneless Wings bundle has it all. 10 Boneless Wings. Curly Fries. And a draft of domestic beer. Only $13.99! 

Wanna skip the beer? No problem. Get 10 Boneless
Wings and Curly Fries for $11.99!

*Available dine in at participating U.S. locations only. Valid for a limited time only on domestic beer noted in the Hooters Beer Menu. Discount applied to food, not alcohol. Available for guests aged 21+. Please drink responsibly. ©2021 Bud Light® and Budweiser® are registered trademarks of Anheuser-Busch. Not valid in Virginia, Maryland and Illinois.

node.text: The @thenotoriousmma fight is almost on. And the shots will be flowing. 💥 Catch #UFC264 with us TONIGHT at select locations! Full Hooters locations list is at the link in our bio.
